description:
Hairstylist Sunnie Brook talks about the glam (and not so glam) side of celebrity hairdressing—and shares some amazing advice she got from her dad. Plus, we talk about beauty products that cause air pollution; in-flight air pollution; and some highlighter and mascara tips that may just blow your mind.
